ApplicantAgentSummary.description:
Single agent's role in this case as projected for the applicant view (EU AI Act Art. 13; OMB M-24-10; ai-integration.md Â§12.1-Â§12.2 line 592-604). The applicant has the right to know that AI participated and in what capacity, but NOT to know the model identifier, version, internal autonomy posture, or proprietary configuration. This shape carries only the disclosure-load-bearing fields.

 <details><summary>JSON schema</summary>

 ```json
{
  "description": "Single agent's role in this case as projected for the applicant view (EU AI Act Art. 13; OMB M-24-10; ai-integration.md Â§12.1-Â§12.2 line 592-604). The applicant has the right to know that AI participated and in what capacity, but NOT to know the model identifier, version, internal autonomy posture, or proprietary configuration. This shape carries only the disclosure-load-bearing fields.",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "displayName",
    "roleInDecision"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "confidence": {
      "description": "Reported calibrated confidence of the agent's contribution to this case in [0,1]. Optional â€” surfaced only when the agent reported a confidence and disclosure policy permits showing it; absent otherwise.",
      "type": "number",
      "maximum": 1.0,
      "minimum": 0.0
    },
    "displayName": {
      "description": "Plain-language agent label suitable for applicant rendering (\"Eligibility Assistant\", not `claude-sonnet-4-20250514`). Open prose â€” the staff `AgentView.modelIdentifier` is intentionally NOT projected here.",
      "examples": [
        "Eligibility Assistant"
      ],
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1,
      "x-wos": {
        "openStringKind": "prose"
      }
    },
    "roleInDecision": {
      "description": "Closed-no-extension role classification matching the disclosure obligation. `advisory` is suggest-only or read-only assistance; `primary` is the agent that produced the determination input (autonomous or supervised); `fallback` is an agent that ran only when an upstream actor failed. The applicant has authority to know which of the three roles the AI played â€” closed by design so the disclosure cannot drift into vendor-specific labels.",
      "examples": [
        "advisory"
      ],
      "enum": [
        "advisory",
        "primary",
        "fallback"
      ]
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
 ```
 </details>

