AssertionGateResult.description:
Single assertion-gate evaluation result (governance Â§5.4; workflow-governance.md:293-305). Each pipeline stage's gate evaluation produces one of these â€” closed-taxonomy gate kind + pass/fail boolean + structured evidence references. Embedded as an optional array on `ReasoningTierRecord.assertionGates` so an auditor walking the reasoning trace can answer "which gate kind failed at this stage and what evidence backs the failure?" without re-deriving from open-prose `criteriaChecked.detail`.

 <details><summary>JSON schema</summary>

