Per-output confidence record (ai-integration.md Â§7.1; ai-integration.md:419-431 â€” "Every agent output MUST be accompanied by a ConfidenceReport"). Closed structural shape carrying the agent's calibrated probability that the output is correct, decay state, and the cumulative-confidence rolling window for multi-step interactions (ai-integration.md Â§7.7). Embedded as an optional field on Reasoning-tier and Narrative-tier records when an agent produced the output the record describes.

 <details><summary>JSON schema</summary>

